        <p>Another aspect of our original Care Plan was that members had to select at least three goals, which broke down into multiple steps and tasks. And each step, task, and goal was reviewed every ten weeks in a lengthy, multi-step process that left members and staff confused and frustrated. This review process was unwieldy and so far off from how members think about goal setting. As part of this initiative to redesign Care Plans, I worked with our clinical team to make them simpler and more aligned to our user feedback.</p>


        <div class="card card--list card--blue">
