        <p>Members also now have the ability to write, edit, replace, and mark a goal complete in real-time, instead of once every ten weeks during review time. This makes the goal setting experience flexible and closer to life, because it accounts for the chaos and constant change in a member's life. They also have the ability to see their goal history, which they couldn't do before without the help of a counselor. These changes open the door for us to celebrate their progress and keep them engaged in a positive way.</p>

