        <h2 class="article__subheader">Staff Experience</h2>

        <p>Transparency and simplicity were the driving forces when redesigning the staff workflow. Before, they did not have a holistic view of the goals each member in their cohort were working on. They instead had to view goals at the individual level, and then piece together the information themselves. With this new design, they can now see goals at the group and individual level, which helps them better prepare for their group sessions. They can now go in confidently knowing what all their members are working on, and can facilitate discussions, create connections, and surface opportunities for them to help each other.</p>

