        <p>On a member's profile page, staff can see a timeline of all the actions taken by both member and counselor, to promote accountability and transparency. They can see when a goal has been added or changed, and who made the update. This level of reporting sets the stage for recommendations, to give staff more insight into a member's progress and how they can help them set and achieve their goals.</p>

