        <h3 class="article__heading">03. Next Steps</h3>

        <p>The next steps are to further test this approach with members and staff, to gain insight into what works and what we need to tweak. We will then pilot it among a small subset of staff and members, so we can learn and refine before we release to the larger group. My team and I are all excited to measure its impact on the organization and the member experience at Groups, which we believe will be highly impactful. By releasing this new version of Care Plans, we are providing members and staff with an experience that more closely aligns with their needs. Ultimately, this means a smarter, more holistic and realistic approach to goal setting, which is a win for everyone. which is a huge step forward for our members, staff, and business.</p>
